    type: "mcq",
    prompt: "A patient is scheduled for a 5-hour posterior spinal fusion in the prone position. Preoperative assessment reveals a Stage 2 pressure injury over the right iliac crest from a prior hospitalization. Which action is most important before positioning this patient?",
    setup: "",
