    type: "mcq",
    prompt: "Two patients have identical Stage 2 pressure injuries. Patient A is well-nourished with normal immune function. Patient B is malnourished and on immunosuppressive therapy. Based on epidermal cell turnover physiology, what is the MOST accurate prediction about their healing timelines?",
